assessment_details.task_description:
This final piece is an individual reflection based upon the course materials. It is 2000 words in length (excluding abstract & reference list). It will be submitted by a specified date during the exam period. You are required to write in the first person, and describe why selected course materials were helpful in developing your insight into service leadership in hospitality. You will select TWO course materials from the list below:

the experience of working together on your group assessment;

the lectures as part of the eight 'Blocks';

a case study discussed during the eight 'Blocks';

an activity during the eight 'Blocks';

a chapter from the required resource (Northouse 2013);

a chapter from one of the recommended resources (Yukl 2013; Hughes et al 2012; Manning et al (2012).

Submission to the FCRC by Hard Copy AND electronically via Blackboard

Further information will be posted to our course Blackboard site and discussed in class.
